Protocol for defining A/B testing methods. @since: 1804.0

– updateCacheWithSuccess:error: required method

Download experience values from the server and map the configuration into AI in-memory cache

– getABTestConsentIdentifier required method

This gives the AbTest Consent key for DeviceStorageConsentHandle.

- (nonnull NSString *)getABTestConsentIdentifier

Return Value

a NSString value which should be used as Identifier for ABTest Consent

Availability

1804

Discussion

Note: Only Consent Definitions containing this key will be considered for ABTest Handling. If no such key is found then the app will crash.
